OL,3,GOPINIONCA change in the weather for
OL,4,CUTV?
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt looks like there's been a change to
OL,7,FUTV's weekend weather arrangements.
OL,9,FNormally UTV forecasts at the weekend
OL,10,Fare voiced out-of-vision by a
OL,11,Fjournalist.
OL,13,FToday there was an in-vision forecast
OL,14,Ffrom Tori Lacey at ITV's northern
OL,15,Fweather hub.
OL,17,FTori ` in line with the practice of
OL,18,Frecent years ` also provided forecasts
OL,19,Ffor the Granada TV, Calendar/Yorkshire
OL,20,FTV, Tyne Tees TV and Border TV regions.
