OL,3,GOPINIONCA change in the weather for
OL,4,CUTV?
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt remains to be seen if this is a
OL,7,Fpermanent change to the arrangements.
OL,9,FBut if it is, it is welcome.
OL,11,FThe out-of-vision forecasts at the
OL,12,Fweekend are disengaging at best and
OL,13,Fsimply tedious and boring at worst.
OL,15,FIf UTV does not consider 7-day local
OL,16,Fweather presentation to be an
OL,17,Fappropriate use of resources, then a
OL,18,Fproper forecast from one of ITV's hubs
OL,19,Fis preferable.
