OL,3,GOPINIONCA change in the weather for
OL,4,CUTV?
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt will become apparent on Sunday and
OL,7,Fover the coming weekends if this change
OL,8,Fis permanent.
OL,10,FIt may also mean a further reduction by
OL,11,Fstealth in the remaining UTV branding.
OL,13,FTonight's forecast began with an
OL,14,FITV-branded caption.
OL,16,FUTV branding is, of course, now
OL,17,Fconfined to local output such as UTV
OL,18,FLive and UTV Life.
